        <h2>
            统治史（卷一）：古代的王权和帝国——从苏美尔到罗马（修订版）的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 3 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4450950">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4450950/" class="title-link">翻译的专业水准不高</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4450950"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/mzhangjian/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3347752-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/mzhangjian/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">壹零时光</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-11-08"
      class="main-meta">2010-11-08 10:35:48</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4450950_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  从出版社定的，昨天刚刚拿到。读起来有点失望，虽然暂时还没找到英文原版，但总觉得翻译得不是很到位。后来网上搜索了下，马百亮只是上海海洋大学的大学英语部教师，毕竟并非政治学、社会学科班出生，对一些术语的把握会有欠缺。建议有条件的朋友，结合着英文原版阅读。原版是...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4450950/#comments">(17回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">24有用 / 4没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            华东师范大学出版社2010版</span>
