            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="35761164">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">查理七世翻译成路易七世我也是醉了，这就是“修订版”？</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-07-30 14:07</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                查理七世翻译成路易七世我也是醉了，这就是“修订版”？
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35761164/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2015-07-30 14:07
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
